E-Learning Portal

A simple website made using HTML, CSS and JS for the front end and PHP, MySQL for the back-end where a user can login using his credentials and can get the course videos or links to any of the course videos of his choice.

I contributed to this project by working on front-end i.e. creating static pages.

Cricket Statistics and Analysis

The main idea behind this project was to create a web page to display cricket player statistics. These statistics are scraped from the internet and then data cleaning and munging is done so as to use this data for further analysis. The data was further used to display player statistics and his achievements in international cricket.

They can also be graphically visualised on the webpage.

Movie Recommendation System

A movie recommendation system using kaggle imdb data set, which basically recommends movies to the users based on collaborative filtering, demographic filtering and Content based filtering.

Retail Store Management System

A simple user interface was made using C# which was connected to Oracle Database and user can trade and bills are created for the items sold and bought by the user.

I contributed to this project by creating the database and writing queries for CRUD operations.

Simulation of Dijkstra's Algorithm using Java Applet

User can create nodes on the panel, draw edges and assign weights and then when the algorithm is run it creates a path from the source node to all the other destinations in the smallest path available.

University Eligibility Predictor

A system implemented in C++ where the student after giving his marks as the input after selecting the college of his choice will get to know whether he is eligible or not for that particular college.

Digit Recognizer

A Deep Learning Model which recognizes the hand written images of digits. PyTorch Framwork was used and both an ANN and a CNN model was created to recognize those digits. Accuracy:

Using ANN: 97.45% Using CNN: 99.01%

BlockChain Working Model

A prototype to demonstrate how working of block-chain technology happens under the hood. With a limited knowledge of the block-chain technology I simply tried to create a prototype which can help beginners like me to get familiar with the working of this technology.

Restaurant Recommendation System

A Recommender system which recommends the restaurants.
